# Normalize line endings. The build-step (build.ps1) rewrites the STCTI.<Map> mission
# files on every run; pinning text files to LF keeps git diffs free of line-ending churn
# so real logic drift stays visible. Arma reads LF and CRLF equally.
* text=auto
*.sqf text eol=lf
*.ext text eol=lf
*.hpp text eol=lf
*.sqm text eol=lf
*.md  text eol=lf
